h HTML head, meta, fonts, body wrapper\n   268→\n   269→**Validate:**\n   270→- [ ] `npm run dev` starts without errors\n   271→- [ ] `/en/`, `/hi/`, `/gu/` routes all render\n   272→- [ ] Tailwind CSS works (test with a utility class)\n   273→- [ ] i18n utility functions return correct translations\n   274→- [ ] Directory structure matches plan\n   275→- [ ] Git commit: `feat(scaffold): T1 — Astro project with i18n and Tailwind`\n   276→\n   277→---\n   278→\n   279→### - [ ] V1: Gate — Verify Project Foundation\n   280→\n   281→**Type:** Verification | **Model:** claude-sonnet-4-6 | **Depends on:** T1\n   282→\n   283→**Knowledge Base:**\n   284→- progress.md — read T1 handover\n   285→- All files created by T1\n   286→\n   287→**Checks:**\n   288→- [ ] `npm run build` succeeds\n   289→- [ ] All 3 language routes generate static HTML\n   290→- [ ] Tailwind classes render correctly in dev\n   291→- [ ] i18n functions work (getTranslations returns correct lang)\n   292→- [ ] TypeScript compiles without errors\n   293→- [ ] Directory structure matches Common Knowledge spec\n   294→- [ ] If issues found → create FX-1 + VFX-1 in Appendix\n   295→\n   296→---\n   297→\n   298→## PHASE 3 — Design System\n   299→\n   300→### - [ ] T2: Create Global Styles, Color System, Typography, Layouts\n   301→\n   302→**Type:** Build | **Model:** claude-opus-4-6 | **Depends on:** V1\n   303→\n   304→**Knowledge Base:**\n   305→- R1 report (color palette, typography, design direction)\n   306→- Tailwind CSS v4 customization docs\n   307→- site-config.ts (created by T1)\n   308→\n   309→**Do:**\n   310→1. Configure Tailwind theme extensions in `src/styles/global.css`:\n   311→   - Colors: gold (#C9A84C), saffron (#FF9933), purple (#6F4278), indigo (#2E2B59), cream (#FFFDF0), maroon (#72001B)\n   312→   - Typography: System fonts + Google Fonts (serif for headings, sans for body)\n   313→   - Support for Devanagari (Hindi) and Gujarati scripts\n   314→2. Create CSS custom properties for