e\n   478→   - Introduction section\n   479→   - Benefits grid\n   480→   - Process walkthrough (numbered steps)\n   481→   - FAQ accordion\n   482→   - Related services\n   483→   - CTA: \"Book This Service\"\n   484→   - Breadcrumbs\n   485→4. Create `src/pages/[lang]/services/index.astro` — services listing\n   486→5. Create `src/pages/[lang]/services/[slug].astro` — dynamic service page\n   487→6. Create placeholder English content for all 12 services at `src/content/services/en/`\n   488→7. Create `getStaticPaths()` that generates all service x language combinations\n   489→\n   490→**Validate:**\n   491→- [ ] All 12 service pages render correctly\n   492→- [ ] Dynamic routing works for all slugs\n   493→- [ ] FAQ accordion expands/collapses\n   494→- [ ] Breadcrumbs show correct path\n   495→- [ ] Related services link to correct pages\n   496→- [ ] Git commit: `feat(pages): T6 — 12 service landing pages with dynamic routing`\n   497→\n   498→---\n   499→\n   500→### - [ ] T7: Build Blog System — Listing Page and Post Template\n   501→\n   502→**Type:** Build | **Model:** claude-opus-4-6 | **Depends on:** V2\n   503→\n   504→**Do:**\n   505→1. Create `src/schemas/blog-content.schema.ts`:\n   506→   - slug, title, excerpt, author, date, category, tags\n   507→   - heroImage, content (markdown), readingTime\n   508→   - seo: { title, description, keywords }\n   509→   - relatedServices[]\n   510→2. Create `src/layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro`:\n   511→   - Featured image\n   512→   - Title, date, author, reading time, category\n   513→   - Content body (rendered markdown)\n   514→   - Social sharing buttons\n   515→   - Related posts\n   516→   - CTA: \"Book a Consultation\"\n   517→3. Create `src/pages/[lang]/blog/index.astro`:\n   518→   - Blog post grid with featured images\n   519→   - Category filter\n   520→   - Pagination\n   521→4. Create `src/pages/[lang]/blog/[slug].astro` — individual blog post\n   522→5. Create 2 placeholder blog posts in English to tes