{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q4w2oBezovmMjRrLn1AQuw","type":"tool_result","content":"     9→## Common Knowledge\n    10→\n    11→### Project Overview\n    12→Multilingual (English, Hindi, Gujarati) astrology website for **Pandit Shree Mahadev Joshi** — \"Believe Astrology\". Based in Ahmedabad, Gujarat, expanding to Mumbai and US. Built with Astro framework (referencing Nilay website architecture for i18n patterns). Must be SEO-optimized for Google, JustDial, social media. Zen philosophy: clean, modular, elegant, trustworthy.\n    13→\n    14→### Astrologer Info\n    15→- **Name:** Pandit Shree Mahadev Joshi\n    16→- **Brand:** Believe Astrology — \"Be Better with Connect to Nature\"\n    17→- **Tagline:** \"Astrology is not about predicting a fixed fate, but about understanding the weather of the cosmos so you can sail your boat with wisdom.\"\n    18→- **Experience:** 20+ years Vedic Astrology & Spiritual Consultation\n    19→- **Services:** Vedic Astrology & Kundli Reading, Horoscope Analysis & Predictions, Marriage/Career/Finance/Health Guidance, Vastu Consultation, Gemstone Recommendations, Karma & Life-Purpose Counselling, Pancha Tatva Balancing, Seven Chakras Balancing, Vedic Spiritual Poojas, Vedic Karma-Kand Yagnas, Maha-Mrutunjay Mantra Anushthan, Mantras Chanting\n    20→- **Contact:** mahadevjoshi91@gmail.com | +91 8154992727 (WhatsApp)\n    21→- **Consultations:** In-person + Zoom/WhatsApp (global)\n    22→\n    23→### Architecture Context (from Nilay Website Reference)\n    24→- **Framework:** Astro 5.x with static site generation\n    25→- **i18n:** URL-based routing `/en/`, `/hi/`, `/gu/` with JSON translation files\n    26→- **Content:** JSON content collections with Zod schemas, per-language directories\n    27→- **Components:** Layout → Sections → Features pattern\n    28→- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4\n    29→- **SEO:** hreflang tags, canonical URLs, JSON-LD schema markup, sitemap\n    30→- **Deployment:** Vercel + GitHub\n    31→\n    32→### Design Direction (from Research)\n    33→- **Theme:** Hybrid — light pages with dark celestial hero sections\n    34→- **Colors:** Deep Gold (#C9A84C), Saffron (#FF9933), Royal Purple (#6F4278), Deep Indigo (#2E2B59), Cream (#FFFDF0), Deep Maroon (#72001B)\n    35→- **Feel:** Trustworthy, zen tranquility, Hindu/astrology resonance, elegant, high-class\n    36→- **Competitor Gap:** Most Ahmedabad astrology sites are outdated/cluttered — modern design = instant differentiation\n    37→\n    38→### Key Files\n    39→| File | Role |\n    40→|------|------|\n    41→| `astro.config.mjs` | Astro config with i18n, sitemap, Tailwind |\n    42→| `src/content/i18n/{en,hi,gu}.json` | Translation strings per language |\n    43→| `src/content/services/{lang}/` | Service content per language |\n    44→| `src/pages/[lang]/` | Language-routed pages |\n    45→| `src/components/` | Reusable UI components |\n    46→| `src/layouts/` | Page layout templates |\n    47→| `src/styles/` | Global styles and Tailwind config |\n    48→| `src/data/` | Static data (testimonials, blog metadata) |\n    49→| `src/utils/i18n.ts` | i18n helper functions |\n    50→| `public/images/` | Hero images, icons, placeholders |\n    51→| `.tasks/mahi-astro/reports/` | Research HTML reports |\n    52→\n    53→### Preferences\n    54→- **Code style:** Max 600 lines/file. Simple, flat, readable. No over-engineering.\n    55→- **Tests:** Playwright E2E tests for critical flows. Unit tests for utilities.\n    56→- **Commits:** `feat(scope):`, `fix(scope):`, `verify(scope):`, `chore:`\n    57→- **Models:** Opus for build/research, Sonnet for verify/fix\n    58→- **Reports:** Zen HTML format with citations, tabs, ASCII diagrams\n    59→- **Languages:** en (default), hi, gu — with fallback to English\n    60→\n    61→### Task Handover Protocol\n    62→After each task, update `progress.md` with:\n    63→1. What was done (files created/modified)\n    64→2. Key decisions made and why\n    65→3. Known issues or gotchas\n    66→4. What the next task needs to know\n    67→\n    68→---"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"1793bb31-c899-4e1c-9140-244ec53d3ca8","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/tasks.md","content":"## Common Knowledge\n\n### Project Overview\nMultilingual (English, Hindi, Gujarati) astrology website for **Pandit Shree Mahadev Joshi** — \"Believe Astrology\". Based in Ahmedabad, Gujarat, expanding to Mumbai and US. Built with Astro framework (referencing Nilay website architecture for i18n patterns). Must be SEO-optimized for Google, JustDial, social media. Zen philosophy: clean, modular, elegant, trustworthy.\n\n### Astrologer Info\n- **Name:** Pandit Shree Mahadev Joshi\n- **Brand:** Believe Astrology — \"Be Better with Connect to Nature\"\n- **Tagline:** \"Astrology is not about predicting a fixed fate, but about understanding the weather of the cosmos so you can sail your boat with wisdom.\"\n- **Experience:** 20+ years Vedic Astrology & Spiritual Consultation\n- **Services:** Vedic Astrology & Kundli Reading, Horoscope Analysis & Predictions, Marriage/Career/Finance/Health Guidance, Vastu Consultation, Gemstone Recommendations, Karma & Life-Purpose Counselling, Pancha Tatva Balancing, Seven Chakras Balancing, Vedic Spiritual Poojas, Vedic Karma-Kand Yagnas, Maha-Mrutunjay Mantra Anushthan, Mantras Chanting\n- **Contact:** mahadevjoshi91@gmail.com | +91 8154992727 (WhatsApp)\n- **Consultations:** In-person + Zoom/WhatsApp (global)\n\n### Architecture Context (from Nilay Website Reference)\n- **Framework:** Astro 5.x with static site generation\n- **i18n:** URL-based routing `/en/`, `/hi/`, `/gu/` with JSON translation files\n- **Content:** JSON content collections with Zod schemas, per-language directories\n- **Components:** Layout → Sections → Features pattern\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4\n- **SEO:** hreflang tags, canonical URLs, JSON-LD schema markup, sitemap\n- **Deployment:** Vercel + GitHub\n\n### Design Direction (from Research)\n- **Theme:** Hybrid — light pages with dark celestial hero sections\n- **Colors:** Deep Gold (#C9A84C), Saffron (#FF9933), Royal Purple (#6F4278), Deep Indigo (#2E2B59), Cream (#FFFDF0), Deep Maroon (#72001B)\n- **Feel:** Trustworthy, zen tranquility, Hindu/astrology resonance, elegant, high-class\n- **Competitor Gap:** Most Ahmedabad astrology sites are outdated/cluttered — modern design = instant differentiation\n\n### Key Files\n| File | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `astro.config.mjs` | Astro config with i18n, sitemap, Tailwind |\n| `src/content/i18n/{en,hi,gu}.json` | Translation strings per language |\n| `src/content/services/{lang}/` | Service content per language |\n| `src/pages/[lang]/` | Language-routed pages |\n| `src/components/` | Reusable UI components |\n| `src/layouts/` | Page layout templates |\n| `src/styles/` | Global styles and Tailwind config |\n| `src/data/` | Static data (testimonials, blog metadata) |\n| `src/utils/i18n.ts` | i18n helper functions |\n| `public/images/` | Hero images, icons, placeholders |\n| `.tasks/mahi-astro/reports/` | Research HTML reports |\n\n### Preferences\n- **Code style:** Max 600 lines/file. Simple, flat, readable. No over-engineering.\n- **Tests:** Playwright E2E tests for critical flows. Unit tests for utilities.\n- **Commits:** `feat(scope):`, `fix(scope):`, `verify(scope):`, `chore:`\n- **Models:** Opus for build/research, Sonnet for verify/fix\n- **Reports:** Zen HTML format with citations, tabs, ASCII diagrams\n- **Languages:** en (default), hi, gu — with fallback to English\n\n### Task Handover Protocol\nAfter each task, update `progress.md` with:\n1. What was done (files created/modified)\n2. Key decisions made and why\n3. Known issues or gotchas\n4. What the next task needs to know\n\n---","numLines":60,"startLine":9,"totalLines":1171}}}
