nterpret your destiny, personality, strengths, and weaknesses. Astrologers can provide insights into various aspects of your life, including career, relationships, and wealth.\n2. **Navigating Challenges:** It helps you identify your good and bad times. Use it to organize your life better and navigate through ups and downs.\n3. **Personalized Remedies:** Your Kundli prescribes solutions and remedies customized for you. It aids in reducing the impact of malefic planetary influences in your Natal Chart, allowing you to better utilize the benefits ruled by the favorable planets.\n4. **Life Decisions:** From choosing the right life partner to exploring new career opportunities, starting a business, or ensuring harmony in your present, your kundli becomes a guiding light at every step.\n5. **Spiritual Insight:** Vedic Astrology (Kundli Analysis) offers a karmic blueprint through ancient methods and spiritual insight. Sessions are personalized, intuitive, and designed to guide your soul journey.\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ Process to Get a Kundli Reading\n\n1. **Provide Birth Details:** Ordering your free Janam Kundali analysis is an easy and simple task as long as you know your birth details. Simply enter your full name, date of birth, time, and place of birth.\n2. **Precision Matters:** In Vedic Astrology, the Ascendant (Lagna) changes every two hours. Even a 5-minute difference can change your divisional charts (Vargas) completely.\n3. **Chart Generation:** A complete Vedic birth chart is generated with Rasi, Navamsa, planetary positions, Vimshottari Dasha periods, Yogas, and more.\n4. **Remedies Provided:** Remedies may include gemstone wearing, mantra chanting, performing pujas, charity, yoga, meditation, and more.\n\n---\n\n## 🔮 2025–2026 Predictions & Trends\n\n- The year 2026 is predicted to be powerful and transformative for career journeys, enlightened by favorable planetary energies. Saturn, the main planet responsible for career ups and downs, will remain in Pisces sign all year long.\n- Comprehensive 2026 yearly horoscopes are available for all zodiac signs covering career growth, relationships, wealth prospects, and health outlook.\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 Popular Platforms Offering Free/Premium Kundli Services\n\n| Platform | Features |\n|---|---|\n| **OnlineJyotish.com** | Uses Swiss Ephemeris with Lahiri Ayanamsa (Chitra Paksha) for precise calculations. |\n| **AstroSage.com** | Introduced free Kundali software around 15 years ago, providing 100% free Kundli reading. |\n| **Astroyogi.com** | Trusted by millions worldwide, their free online Kundli generator reveals accurate insights into planetary positions, doshas, and key life events. |\n| **VedicRishi.in** | Provides 100% original and accurate Kundali predictions in multiple Indian languages. |\n| **Indastro.com** | Offers detailed life reading, marriage reports, career analysis, and 2026 love/marriage reports. |\n\n---\n\nWhether you're looking for free online chart generation or premium personalized consultations, these Kundli reading services can offer deep insights into your life path using the time-tested principles of Vedic astrology."],"durationSeconds":37.57237975}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XUNM8iJGmsr8eC1TsrNpkm","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Vastu consultation service description benefits process what is Vastu Shastra\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Vastu shastra - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vastu_shastra\"},{\"title\":\"Vastu Consultant, Vaastu Expert Online, Vaastu Shastra Guru, Vasthu\",\"url\":\"https://vastuconsultant.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Vaastu Sanjivanii - Harmonizing Spaces, Transforming Lives\",\"url\":\"https://www.vaastusanjivanii.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Vastu Services,Indian Vastu Services,Vaastu Services,Vaastu Shastra Services,Vastu Services India\",\"url\":\"https://www.vaastu-shastra.com/vastu-services.html\"},{\"title\":\"Personalised Vastu Consultant in Bangalore | Vaastu Vidwan\",\"url\":\"https://vaastuvidwan.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Vastu Shastra [What Is It & How You Can Apply]\",\"url\":\"https://www.vastushastraguru.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Online Vastu Consultation | Most Accurate & Result Oriented\",\"url\":\"https://vaastudevayah.com/online-vastu-consultation.php\"},{\"title\":\"AppliedVastu® : Trusted Vastu Shastra Consultancy | Vastu Course | Vastu Tips | Vastu App\",\"url\":\"https://www.appliedvastu.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Vastu Consultation with Instructions and Products -\",\"url\":\"https://vastucreations.com/product/vastu-consultation-with-instructions-and-products-2/\"},{\"title\":\"Online Vastu Consultation\",\"url\":\"https://www.askacharya.com/index.php/vastu/vastu-consultation\"}]\n\nHere's a comprehensive overview of **Vastu Shastra** and Vastu consultation services based on the search results:\n\n---\n\n## What is Vastu Shastra?\n\nOriginating in ancient India, Vastu Shastra (Sanskrit: वास्तु शास्त्र, vāstu śāstra – literally \"science of architecture\") is a traditional Hindu system of architecture based on ancient texts that describe principles of design, layout, measurements, ground preparation, space arrangement, and spatial geometry.\n\nThe designs aim to integrate architecture with nature, the relative functions of various parts of the structure, and ancient beliefs utilising geometric patterns (yantra), symmetry, and directional alignments.\n\nVastu Shastra is described as an ancient Indian architectural science that harmonizes the energy flow within a structure, bringing harmony, peace, and success to its occupants. It is based on the principle that the elements of nature, such as earth, water, fire, air, and space, have a profound impact on the energy vibrations within a space.\n\n### The Five Elements\n\nThe Five Elements — Water, Fire, Earth, Space & Air — are the fundamental elements of Vastu Shastra. Understanding their significance is essential. Each element is a distinct kind of energy based on the direction it is facing, and knowing how they relate to one another is vital to produce auspicious or inauspicious energy in the environment.\n\n---\n\n## Vastu Consultation Services\n\n### What Does a Consultation Involve?\n\nDuring Vastu consultation, an expert provides necessary details pertaining to site, plot, soil, etc., with full scrutiny and examination. Site consultation involves site visit, analyzing typography, soil testing, examining directions, and environment.\n\nBy analyzing the layout, orientation, and energy patterns of your space, experts provide insightful recommendations to optimize the flow of positive energy, creating an environment conducive to growth and well-being.\n\n### Types of Consultation\n\n1. **On-Site Consultation:** On-site evaluation and compass reading of your premises will be conducted at a mutually agreed time and day. These evaluations usually take 1–2 hours.\n\n2. **Off-Site / Online Consultation:** Online Vastu Analysis is a simple yet effective system which enables you to take the benefit of Vastu Shastra anywhere in the world. It is an effortless process which requires basic details of your property and your family, followed by doorstep delivery of Vastu Report & Vastu remedies.\n\n---\n\n## The Consultation Process\n\nThe typical process involves several key steps:\n\n1. **Initial Contact & Details Sharing:** The Vastu process starts with a proposal about the site. An initial phone conversation or details via email about the site to be consulted will help understand your requirement and enable a fee quote.\n\n2. **Floor Plan & Direction Analysis:** At stage two, a floor plan with accurate direction, details on the surrounding of the site, history of the premises, and a brief on your goals & priorities are needed.\n\n3. **In-Depth Property Analysis:** The team of experts works in-depth with your property's layouts, analyzing every aspect following Vastu's principles, matching it with the problems confronted by the residents, and developing solutions to the Vastu issues. The primary goal is to prepare Vastu solutions that are easy to implement yet efficient.\n\n4. **Report & Remedies:** You receive a detailed Vastu Consultation including a Vastu Manual custom prepared for your site, which has all the information required to firstly align the place as per Vastu and then serve as reference to maintain the place.\n\n5. **Follow-Up Support:** Follow-up options that monitor the effectiveness of the Vastu implementation are provided, including free backup services for one year after consultation for the same premises.\n\n---\n\n## Claimed Benefits of Vastu Consultation\n\nVastu Shastra is said to benefit your ongoing success and prosperity, bringing harmony, peace, and fulfillment.\n\nVastu consultation is said to play a crucial role in enhancing the positive energy in your living or working space. Experts assess various factors such as entrance placements, room arrangements, and color schemes to create a balanced environment that nurtures positivity and vitality.\n\nCommon **Vastu remedies** include: the use of Vastu products, rearranging furniture, making adjustments to room layouts, and utilizing elements like colors, symbols, and crystals to enhance positive energy in a space.\n\n---\n\n## Important Note on Scientific Standing\n\nIt should be noted that Vastu Shastra is considered a pseudoscience by Narendra Nayak, head of the Federation of Indian Rationalist Associations. Astronomer Jayant Narlikar states that while Vastu Shastra has rules about integrating architecture with its ambience, the alleged harm or benefits being marketed have \"no logical connection to environment.\"\n\nScholar Vibhuti Chakrabarti has noted that in contemporary India, some offer Vastu consulting services projecting it as a \"religious tradition\" rather than an \"architectural methodology.\"\n\n---\n\nThis should give you a well-rounded understanding of what Vastu Shastra is, how the consultation process works, and the different perspectives on its claims and validity.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"f1d028a5-9fe9-434a-89fd-9319f1e36d3c","tool_use_result":{"query":"Vastu consultation service description benefits process what is Vastu Shastra","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Jv3gwUxSJcw1AqsnQLTqPF","content":[{"title":"Vastu shastra - Wikipedia","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vastu_shastra"},{"title":"Vastu Consultant, Vaastu Expert Online, Vaastu Shastra Guru, Vasthu","url":"https://vastuconsultant.com/"},{"title":"Vaastu Sanjivanii - Harmonizing Spaces, Transforming Lives","url":"https://www.vaastusanjivanii.com/"},{"title":"Vastu Services,Indian Vastu Services,Vaastu Services,Vaastu Shastra Services,Vastu Services India","url":"https://www.vaastu-shastra.com/vastu-services.html"},{"title":"Personalised Vastu Consultant in Bangalore | Vaastu Vidwan","url":"https://vaastuvidwan.com/"},{"title":"Vastu Shastra [What Is It & How You Can Apply]","url":"https://www.vastushastraguru.com/