Does a Consultation Involve?\n\nDuring Vastu consultation, an expert provides necessary details pertaining to site, plot, soil, etc., with full scrutiny and examination. Site consultation involves site visit, analyzing typography, soil testing, examining directions, and environment.\n\nBy analyzing the layout, orientation, and energy patterns of your space, experts provide insightful recommendations to optimize the flow of positive energy, creating an environment conducive to growth and well-being.\n\n### Types of Consultation\n\n1. **On-Site Consultation:** On-site evaluation and compass reading of your premises will be conducted at a mutually agreed time and day. These evaluations usually take 1–2 hours.\n\n2. **Off-Site / Online Consultation:** Online Vastu Analysis is a simple yet effective system which enables you to take the benefit of Vastu Shastra anywhere in the world. It is an effortless process which requires basic details of your property and your family, followed by doorstep delivery of Vastu Report & Vastu remedies.\n\n---\n\n## The Consultation Process\n\nThe typical process involves several key steps:\n\n1. **Initial Contact & Details Sharing:** The Vastu process starts with a proposal about the site. An initial phone conversation or details via email about the site to be consulted will help understand your requirement and enable a fee quote.\n\n2. **Floor Plan & Direction Analysis:** At stage two, a floor plan with accurate direction, details on the surrounding of the site, history of the premises, and a brief on your goals & priorities are needed.\n\n3. **In-Depth Property Analysis:** The team of experts works in-depth with your property's layouts, analyzing every aspect following Vastu's principles, matching it with the problems confronted by the residents, and developing solutions to the Vastu issues. The primary goal is to prepare Vastu solutions that are easy to implement yet efficient.\n\n4. **Report & Remedies:** You receive a detailed Vastu Consultation including a Vastu Manual custom prepared for your site, which has all the information required to firstly align the place as per Vastu and then serve as reference to maintain the place.\n\n5. **Follow-Up Support:** Follow-up options that monitor the effectiveness of the Vastu implementation are provided, including free backup services for one year after consultation for the same premises.\n\n---\n\n## Claimed Benefits of Vastu Consultation\n\nVastu Shastra is said to benefit your ongoing success and prosperity, bringing harmony, peace, and fulfillment.\n\nVastu consultation is said to play a crucial role in enhancing the positive energy in your living or working space. Experts assess various factors such as entrance placements, room arrangements, and color schemes to create a balanced environment that nurtures positivity and vitality.\n\nCommon **Vastu remedies** include: the use of Vastu products, rearranging furniture, making adjustments to room layouts, and utilizing elements like colors, symbols, and crystals to enhance positive energy in a space.\n\n---\n\n## Important Note on Scientific Standing\n\nIt should be noted that Vastu Shastra is considered a pseudoscience by Narendra Nayak, head of the Federation of Indian Rationalist Associations. Astronomer Jayant Narlikar states that while Vastu Shastra has rules about integrating architecture with its ambience, the alleged harm or benefits being marketed have \"no logical connection to environment.\"\n\nScholar Vibhuti Chakrabarti has noted that in contemporary India, some offer Vastu consulting services projecting it as a \"religious tradition\" rather than an \"architectural methodology.\"\n\n---\n\nThis should give you a well-rounded understanding of what Vastu Shastra is, how the consultation process works, and the different perspectives on its claims and validity."],"durationSeconds":37.378575875}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AsuYdwB62c9LfbJ8NYNagw","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"gemstone recommendation astrology Jyotish ratna benefits process\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Free Gemstone Recommendation by Date of Birth | Lucky Stone, Rashi Ratna\",\"url\":\"https://myratna.com/gemstone-recommendation.html\"},{\"title\":\"Gem Recommendation according to Horoscope\",\"url\":\"https://myratna.com/article/gem-recommendation-according-to-horoscope\"},{\"title\":\"Gemstone Calculator | Gemstone Finder | Ratna Calculator\",\"url\":\"https://www.drikpanchang.com/jyotisha/gemstone/gemstone-calculator.html\"},{\"title\":\"Gemstone Recommendation based on Date of Birth, Kundli, Problems – Rudraksha Ratna\",\"url\":\"https://www.rudraksha-ratna.com/articles/gemstone-recommendation\"},{\"title\":\"Gemstones for Life, Health and Progress\",\"url\":\"https://www.astrosage.com/gemstones/default.asp\"},{\"title\":\"Online Gemstone Recommendation Services - Pandit Ji On Call\",\"url\":\"https://panditjioncall.com/services/gemstone-recommendation\"},{\"title\":\"Which Gemstone Should I Wear? A Complete Step-by-Step Guide to Finding Your Stone Using Vedic Astrology\",\"url\":\"https://www.jeevanratna.com/post/which-gemstone-should-i-wear-a-complete-step-by-step-guide-to-finding-your-stone-using-vedic-astrol\"},{\"title\":\"Know your Gemstone According to Vedic Astrology\",\"url\":\"https://www.gempundit.com/blog/gemstones-of-vedic-astrology\"},{\"title\":\"Ratna: an introduction to gemstones — Dayanand Jyotish\",\"url\":\"https://www.dayanandjyotish.com/news/ratna-an-introduction-to-gemstones\"},{\"title\":\"Navratna Gemstones Guide: 9 Vedic Astrology Stones & Benefits\",\"url\":\"https://www.gemsroot.com/blogs/guide/9-powerful-and-auspicious-gemstones-of-vedic-astrology\"}]\n\nHere's a comprehensive overview of **Gemstone Recommendation in Jyotish (Vedic Astrology) — Ratna Benefits & Process**:\n\n---\n\n## What Are Jyotish Ratnas?\n\nThe Nav Ratnas (the 9 natural Vedic Gemstones) represent the 9 astrology planets referenced in the ancient Vedic scriptures as the key to counteract negative karmic forces and heal the mind and body. Ratna, known as gemstones, are without a doubt the most commonly prescribed remedy by Vedic Astrologers.\n\n## The Nine Gemstones (Navratnas) & Their Planets\n\nAccording to astrological texts, Ruby is associated with the Sun, Pearl with the Moon, Red Coral with Mars, Yellow Sapphire with Jupiter, Blue Sapphire with Saturn, Diamond with Venus, Hessonite with Rahu, Emerald with Mercury, and Cat's Eye with Ketu. 84 secondary gemstones to these 9 gemstones are also popular, but these 9 gemstones are considered primary gemstones which are used by astrologers to alleviate the effects of afflicted planets.\n\n## Benefits of Wearing Jyotish Gemstones\n\n- Gemstones are known for their powerful astrological benefits in health, wealth, and spiritual growth.\n- Gemstones can lessen the harmful effects of evil planets and bad things that happen when heavenly bodies move around. Gemstone benefits can help with many areas of your life, including your personal life, job, marriage, business, and fitness.\n- A natural, certified gemstone resonating with your benefic planet creates what Jyotish calls *Anukul Graha* — a favourable planetary condition. You may experience this as greater mental clarity, emotional steadiness, or a sense that the right opportunities are finding you more readily.\n\n### Examples of Specific Gemstone Benefits:\n- **Ruby (Sun):** When the Sun is influenced positively in the Jyotish chart, the wearer can enjoy benefits such as brilliance, wealth, fame, and power.\n- **Yellow Sapphire (Jupiter):** Pukhraj Stone holds a special position in astrology with its association with Jupiter, which symbolizes growth, expansion, good fortune, prosperity, healing, and divine miracles. A weak Jupiter can lead to a lack of enthusiasm, pessimism, and consistent struggles, and wearing Pukhraj can help strengthen Jupiter's position in your horoscope.\n- **Blue Sapphire (Saturn):** When Saturn is influenced positively, the wearer can enhance wealth and prosperity and bring instant success in business, jobs, and independent projects. It can also help one be disciplined and patient, and a genuine Blue Sapphire tranquillizes the mind and relieves anxiety and depression.\n\n## The Recommendation Process\n\n### 1. Birth Chart (Kundli) Analysis\nVedic astrology is an ancient science that studies the position of planets at the time of your birth. This forms your birth chart or Kundli, which helps in knowing which gemstone to wear for your success, health, and peace.\n\n### 2. Planetary Position Study\nTo recommend the best gem, it is necessary to study the planetary positions in house 2 and 11 of your Kundli, and to help you neutralize the impact of any non-favourable Yog, appropriate gems can be used.\n\n### 3. Advanced Calculations\nThe process calculates your Lagna, identifies your functional benefics and malefics, checks for Yogakarakas, evaluates your current Mahadasha and Antardasha, and assesses planetary strength using Shadbala — and surfaces the gemstone recommendation that emerges from all of it combined.\n\n### 4. Expert Consultation Is Key\nNot all gemstones are lucky for everyone, and the gemstone suitable for one person might be very harmful for another. This process requires a lot of typical calculations and analysis, so only an expert and experienced astrologer can tell you about the most suitable gemstone.\n\nBasic generalized advice like \"Those with Gemini Ascendent should wear Emerald\" is rather like prescribing one particular medicine for 1/12th of the human race. Everyone's birth chart is different, with many variable factors, and using remedies with a broad application can actually have a detrimental impact — highlighting the need for a knowledgeable astrologer.\n\n## Important Considerations\n\n- **Anukula vs. Pratikula System:** It's recommended to stick to the Anukula system as this is the safest approach and least likely to derive negative results, but there are exceptions. Pratikula gemstones can be used in cases when involved in a favourable yoga in a kendra or kona.\n- **Compatibility:** Gemstones of planets having enmity with each other should not be worn together, because they may develop troubles in your life. The planets which share friendship, their gemstones should be worn together to improve results.\n- **Quality:** Jyotish gems must be of high quality, clear, and should not contain flaws, blemishes, or cracks. Gemstones that are tampered with or artificially made are traditionally not recommended. The size and cut of gems is also of significance.\n- **Classical Sources:** The Rig Veda, Atharva Veda, Garuda Purana, Agni Purana, Bhagavata Purana, and Varahamihira's Brihat Samhita are some of the many texts to be studied for knowledge pertaining to gemstones.\n\n---\n\nIn summary, Jyotish gemstone recommendation is a deeply personalized process rooted in Vedic astrology, requiring careful analysis of one's birth chart, planetary strengths, and current planetary periods. Always consult a qualified Jyotish practitioner before wearing any gemstone.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"4786a25b-a42c-4618-8150-cc0b3abc3ca8","tool_use_result":{"query":"gemstone recommendation astrology Jyotish ratna benefits process","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01WhcKbYxEanntq6AZqDxHpg","content":[{"title":"Free Gemstone Recommendation by Date of Birth | Lucky Stone, Rashi Ratna","url":"https://myratna.com/gemstone-recommendation.html"},{"title":"Gem Recommendation according to Horoscope","url":"https://myratna.com/article/gem-recommendation-according-to-horoscope"},{"title":"Gemstone Calculator | Gems