\nDelivering bite-sized predictions tailored to each zodiac sign on a daily basis is a strong engagement strategy for astrology accounts.\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 Useful Resources\n- **[Feedspot's Top 100 Astrology Blogs 2026](https://bloggers.feedspot.com/astrology_blogs/)** — Features blogs on Vedic astrology, finance, compatibility, life purpose, personal development, and career development.\n- **[GauravDubey.in](https://gauravdubey.in/recent-blog-topics-and-ideas-for-astrology/)** — Extensive list of blog topics for astrology services in 2026.\n- **[AstroSight Digital Marketing Guide](https://astrosight.ai/blog/digital-marketing-for-astrologers)** — A guide on digital marketing strategies for astrologers.\n\nThese topics and strategies should help you build a robust content calendar for your Vedic astrology blog!"],"durationSeconds":29.500883124999994}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016LkhhnkdvSveNG78dW7NAz","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"astrology keywords Hindi Gujarati SEO jyotish kundli rashifal vastu\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"એસ્ટ્રોસેજ એઆઈ જ્યોતીષયો નો મોટો કમાલ,આપ્યા 10 કરોડ સવાલ ના જવાબ\",\"url\":\"https://www.astrosage.com/gujarati/\"},{\"title\":\"ગુજરાતી કુંડળી મફત સૉફ્ટવેર ઓનલાઇન - Kundli in Gujarati\",\"url\":\"https://www.astrosage.com/gujarati/kundli.asp\"},{\"title\":\"Free Horoscope in Gujarati, ગુજરાતીમાં જ્યોતિષ - Clickastro\",\"url\":\"https://www.clickastro.com/free-horoscope-gujarati\"},{\"title\":\"Free Vedic Horoscope (Kundli) | Birth Chart, Planets, Dashas, full report - Online Jyotish\",\"url\":\"https://www.onlinejyotish.com/free-astrology/vedic-horoscope.php\"},{\"title\":\"Kundali | Jatakama | Horoscope | Janma Patrika | Patrika | Janmapatri | Birthchart\",\"url\":\"https://www.drikpanchang.com/jyotisha/kundali/janma-kundali.html\"},{\"title\":\"ગુજરાતી જનમ કુંડળી|Janam Kundali in Gujarati\",\"url\":\"https://m.epanchang.com/janam-kundali-in-gujarati\"},{\"title\":\"Your Trusted and Authentic Vedic Astrology partner since\",\"url\":\"https://www.onlinejyotish.com/\"},{\"title\":\"AstroSage Kundli: AI Astrology - Apps on Google Play\",\"url\":\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ojassoft.astrosage&hl=en\"},{\"title\":\"AI Astrology - Free Online Horoscope & AI-Powered Online Astrologer\",\"url\":\"https://www.astrosage.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Buy Astrology Books in Gujarati | Vedic Astrology Texts\",\"url\":\"https://www.exoticindia.com/book/regionallanguages/gujarati/astrology/2/\"}]\n\nHere are the key findings from the search results regarding **astrology keywords in Hindi and Gujarati for SEO** (covering Jyotish, Kundli, Rashifal, and Vastu):\n\n---\n\n## Top SEO Keywords & Themes in the Astrology Niche\n\n### 🔑 Core Keywords (Hindi & English mix)\nKey terms heavily used across top sites include: **Free Kundli, Horoscope Matching, Rashifal (राशिफल), Today's Horoscope, Online Horoscope, Rahu Kaal, Hindi Kundli, Lal Kitab, Moon Signs**.\n\nAdditional high-traffic keywords include: **Palmistry, Tarot Reading, Vastu, Chinese Astrology, Numerology, Mantra, Chalisa, Aarti, Nadi Astrology, Nakshatra, Kaalsarp Yoga/Dosha, Gemstones Report, Sade Sati Report, Mangal Dosha Report, Varshphal, Vimshottari Dasha**.\n\n### 🔑 Gujarati-Specific Keywords\nIn Gujarati, the key terms are **કુંડળી (Kundali), જ્યોતિષ વિદ્યા (Jyotish Vidya), જન્મ પ્રમાણ પત્ર (birth certificate), and જન્માક્ષર (Janmakshar)**.\n\nClickastro targets Gujarati users with terms like **\"Free Horoscope in Gujarati,\" \"Kundli in Gujarati by date of birth,\" and \"ગુજરાતીમાં જ્યોતિષ\" (Astrology in Gujarati)**.\n\n### 🔑 Yearly/Trending Keywords\nTrending yearly keywords include: **Horoscope 2026, Calendar 2026, Rashifal 2026, daily rashifal, monthly rashiphal, Kundali Matching (Ashtakoota Guna Milap)**.\n\n### 🔑 Vastu Keywords\nVastu Shastra is described as \"an ancient Sanskrit manual of architectural and scientific writings\" and includes topics like layouts of houses, roads, shops, gardens, and temple designs. Key Vastu SEO themes include harmonizing energy flow, directional alignment, prosperity, and **Vastu Doshas** (imbalances causing career obstacles, mental stress, etc.).\n\n### 🔑 Jyotish / Vedic Astrology Keywords\nJyotisha (also called Hindu astrology, Indian astrology, or Vedic astrology) is one of the Vedāṅga — the six assistant disciplines used in Vedic customs.\n\nOnlineJyotish.com targets keywords like **Free Vedic horoscope (Kundli), Panchang, Rashifal, marriage matching, dosha reports & calculators in 14 languages** with \"accurate, city-based timings and reports.\"\n\n### 🔑 Multi-Language Support Keywords\nTop astrology apps support **Hindi, English, Tamil, Telugu, Marathi, Gujarati, Kannada, Malayalam & Bengali languages**.\n\n---\n\n## Top Competing Websites in This Niche\n| Website | Focus |\n|---|---|\n| **AstroSage.com** | AI-powered Kundli, Rashifal, Vastu, multi-language |\n| **OnlineJyotish.com** | Vedic horoscope, Panchang, 14 languages |\n| **ClickAstro.com** | Free Gujarati horoscopes |\n| **DrikPanchang.com** | Kundali, Panchang, Dosha calculators |\n| **ePanchang.com** | Janam Kundali in Gujarati |\n\n---\n\n### Summary of High-Value SEO Keywords\nHere's a consolidated list of keywords to target for Hindi/Gujarati astrology SEO:\n\n- **Hindi**: Kundli, Rashifal, Jyotish, Vastu, Panchang, Rahu Kaal, Mangal Dosha, Sade Sati, Lal Kitab, Horoscope Matching, Nakshatra, Mahadasha\n- **Gujarati**: કુંડળી, રાશિફળ, જ્યોતિષ, વાસ્તુ, જન્માક્ષર, ગુણ મિલાન\n- **English (Indic SEO)**: Free Kundli, Vedic Astrology, Birth Chart, Horoscope 2026, Vastu Shastra, Numerology, Tarot Reading\n\nThese keywords reflect high search volume topics used by the leading astrology platforms in India.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"0408cb60-a62d-4f07-9c2e-f5576386f914","tool_use_result":{"query":"astrology keywords Hindi Gujarati SEO jyotish kundli rashifal vastu","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01PEev6avCgLqNDnQ1FBpCCq","content":[{"title":"એસ્ટ્રોસેજ એઆઈ જ્યોતીષયો નો મોટો કમાલ,આપ્યા 10 કરોડ સવાલ ના જવાબ","url":"https://www.astrosage.com/gujarati/"},{"title":"ગુજરાતી કુંડળી મફત સૉફ્ટવેર ઓનલાઇન - Kundli in Gujarati","url":"https://www.astrosage.com/gujarati/kundli.asp"},{"title":"Free Horoscope in Gujarati, ગુજરાતીમાં જ્યોતિષ - Clickastro","url":"https://www.clickastro.com/free-horoscope-gujarati"},{"title":"Free Vedic Horoscope (Kundli) | Birth Chart, Planets, Dashas, full report - Online Jyotish","url":"https://www.onlinejyotish.com/free-astrology/vedic-horoscope.php"},{"title":"Kundali | Jatakama | Horoscope | Janma Patrika | Patrika | Janmapatri | Birthchart","url":"https://www.drikpanchang.com/jyo