{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Wa1mnfBoFFAntmECiPpo1k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01H2jBp4kSX4jy9qgWxwJCbp","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/marriage-career-finance-health-guidance.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"marriage-career-finance-health-guidance\",\n  \"title\": \"Marriage, Career, Finance & Health Guidance\",\n  \"slug\": \"marriage-career-finance-health-guidance\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"compass\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Navigate life's biggest decisions — marriage compatibility, career direction, financial timing, and health insights through Vedic astrology.\",\n  \"description\": \"Life presents crossroads — choosing a career, selecting a life partner, making financial investments, or addressing health concerns. Vedic astrology offers a unique lens to navigate these pivotal decisions by revealing the planetary influences that shape each area of your life.\\n\\nMarriage & Relationships: Kundli matching (Ashtakoota Guna Milap) evaluates compatibility across 36 points covering temperament, health, prosperity, and emotional connection. Beyond matching, Panditji analyzes the 7th house, Venus placement, and Dasha timing to advise on optimal marriage timing and relationship dynamics.\\n\\nCareer & Professional Growth: The 10th house, its lord, and planets like Saturn and Mercury reveal your vocational strengths. Panditji identifies career paths aligned with your planetary configuration, optimal timing for job changes or business launches, and remedies for professional blocks.\\n\\nFinance & Wealth: The 2nd and 11th houses govern earnings and gains. Analysis of Jupiter, Venus, and wealth-forming Yogas (like Dhana Yoga or Lakshmi Yoga) reveals your financial potential and the best periods for investments, property purchases, and wealth accumulation.\\n\\nHealth & Wellbeing: Each planet governs specific body systems. The 6th house and afflictions to key planets can indicate health tendencies, enabling preventive measures and lifestyle adjustments before issues manifest.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Informed decision-making at life's major crossroads\",\n    \"Compatible partner selection through scientific Kundli matching\",\n    \"Career clarity aligned with innate planetary strengths\",\n    \"Financial timing for maximum return on investments\",\n    \"Preventive health insights from astrological indicators\",\n    \"Holistic life planning with timing for all major milestones\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Birth Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Comprehensive review of houses, planets, and Dashas relevant to your specific concern.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Area-Specific Deep Dive\", \"description\": \"Focused analysis on marriage, career, finance, or health — or all four.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Kundli Matching (if applicable)\", \"description\": \"Detailed compatibility analysis with a potential partner's chart.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Timing Guidance\", \"description\": \"Muhurta (auspicious timing) recommendations for key decisions.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Remedies\", \"description\": \"Specific actions, mantras, or rituals to strengthen weak areas.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"What is Kundli matching and why is it important for marriage?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Kundli matching compares two birth charts across 36 points (Ashtakoota). A score of 18+ is generally considered favorable. It assesses compatibility in health, temperament, children, financial prosperity, and emotional bonding — but it's a guide, not a verdict.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can astrology tell me exactly which career to choose?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Astrology reveals your natural aptitudes, favorable sectors, and optimal timing for career moves. It narrows the field and highlights strengths but works best as a complement to your own interests and practical considerations.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is financial astrology reliable for investment decisions?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Astrological timing can indicate favorable and unfavorable periods for financial ventures. It's a supplementary tool — combine it with proper financial analysis and professional advice for best results.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"marriage astrology\", \"career astrology\", \"financial astrology\", \"health horoscope\", \"kundli matching\", \"muhurta\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"विवाह ज्योतिष\", \"करियर ज्योतिष\", \"कुंडली मिलान\", \"स्वास्थ्य ज्योतिष\", \"धन योग\", \"मुहूर्त\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"લગ્ન જ્યોતિષ\", \"કારકિર્દી જ્યોતિષ\", \"કુંડળી મિલાન\", \"સ્વાસ્થ્ય જ્યોતિષ\", \"મુહૂર્ત\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"horoscope-analysis-predictions\", \"gemstone-recommendations\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"How Astrology Can Guide Your Career Choice: A Vedic Perspective\",\n    \"Kundli Matching for Marriage: Why It Matters and How It Works\",\n    \"Best Astrological Timing for Property and Investment Decisions\",\n    \"Health Indicators in Your Birth Chart: What to Watch For\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":387,"cache_read_input_tokens":81254,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":387,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"6df83f31-7aab-4f3b-8250-6eeff9ef3ced"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01H2jBp4kSX4jy9qgWxwJCbp","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/marriage-career-finance-health-guidance.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"d0300bb1-fef0-4296-95fb-ddcfb37d11f9","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/marriage-career-finance-health-guidance.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"marriage-career-finance-health-guidance\",\n  \"title\": \"Marriage, Career, Finance & Health Guidance\",\n  \"slug\": \"marriage-career-finance-health-guidance\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"compass\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Navigate life's biggest decisions — marriage compatibility, career direction, financial timing, and health insights through Vedic astrology.\",\n  \"description\": \"Life presents crossroads — choosing a career, selecting a life partner, making financial investments, or addressing health concerns. Vedic astrology offers a unique lens to navigate these pivotal decisions by revealing the planetary influences that shape each area of your life.\\n\\nMarriage & Relationships: Kundli matching (Ashtakoota Guna Milap) evaluates compatibility across 36 points covering temperament, health, prosperity, and emotional connection. Beyond matching, Panditji analyzes the 7th house, Venus placement, and Dasha timing to advise on optimal marriage timing and relationship dynamics.\\n\\nCareer & Professional Growth: The 10th house, its lord, and planets like Saturn and Mercury reveal your vocational strengths. Panditji identifies career paths aligned with your planetary configuration, optimal timing for job changes or business launches, and remedies for professional blocks.\\n\\nFinance & Wealth: The 2nd and 11th houses govern earnings and gains. Analysis of Jupiter, Venus, and wealth-forming Yogas (like Dhana Yoga or Lakshmi Yoga) reveals your financial potential and the best periods for investments, property purchases, and wealth accumulation.\\n\\nHealth & Wellbeing: Each planet governs specific body systems. The 6th house and afflictions to key planets can indicate health tendencies, enabling preventive measures and lifestyle adjustments before issues manifest.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Informed decision-making at life's major crossroads\",\n    \"Compatible partner selection through scientific Kundli matching\",\n    \"Career clarity aligned with innate planetary strengths\",\n    \"Financial timing for maximum return on investments\",\n    \"Preventive health insights from astrological indicators\",\n    \"Holistic life planning with timing for all major milestones\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Birth Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Comprehensive review of houses, planets, and Dashas relevant to your specific concern.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Area-Specific Deep Dive\", \"description\": \"Focused analysis on marriage, career, finance, or health — or all four.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Kundli Matching (if applicable)\", \"description\": \"Detailed compatibility analysis with a potential partner's chart.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Timing Guidance\", \"description\": \"Muhurta (auspicious timing) recommendations for key decisions.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Remedies\", \"description\": \"Specific actions, mantras, or rituals to strengthen weak areas.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"What is Kundli matching and why is it important for marriage?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Kundli matching compares two birth charts across 36 points (Ashtakoota). A score of 18+ is generally considered favorable. It assesses compatibility in health, temperament, children, financial prosperity, and emotional bonding — but it's a guide, not a verdict.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can astrology tell me exactly which career to choose?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Astrology reveals your natural aptitudes, favorable sectors, and optimal timing for career moves. It narrows the field and highlights strengths but works best as a complement to your own interests and practical considerations.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is financial astrology reliable for investment decisions?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Astrological timing can indicate favorable and unfavorable periods for financial ventures. It's a supplementary tool — combine it with proper financial analysis and professional advice for best results.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"marriage astrology\", \"career astrology\", \"financial astrology\", \"health horoscope\", \"kundli matching\", \"muhurta\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"विवाह ज्योतिष\", \"करियर ज्योतिष\", \"कुंडली मिलान\", \"स्वास्थ्य ज्योतिष\", \"धन योग\", \"मुहूर्त\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"લગ્ન જ્યોતિષ\", \"કારકિર્દી જ્યોતિષ\", \"કુંડળી મિલાન\", \"સ્વાસ્થ્ય જ્યોતિષ\", \"મુહૂર્ત\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"horoscope-analysis-predictions\", \"gemstone-recommendations\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"How Astrology Can Guide Your Career Choice: A Vedic Perspective\",\n    \"Kundli Matching for Marriage: Why It Matters and How It Works\",\n    \"Best Astrological Timing for Property and Investment Decisions\",\n    \"Health Indicators in Your Birth Chart: What to Watch For\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Wa1mnfBoFFAntmECiPpo1k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WD5F6AAC9n4uj6c18zfrMu","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/vastu-consultation.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"vastu-consultation\",\n  \"title\": \"Vastu Consultation\",\n  \"slug\": \"vastu-consultation\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"home\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Harmonize your living and working spaces with ancient Vastu Shastra principles for positive energy flow, prosperity, and peace.\",\n  \"description\": \"Vastu Shastra — the ancient Indian science of architecture and spatial harmony — teaches that the energy flow within your living and working spaces profoundly influences your health, prosperity, relationships, and peace of mind. Like a cosmic version of environmental design, Vastu aligns your physical spaces with the five fundamental elements (earth, water, fire, air, and space) and the eight cardinal directions.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi offers comprehensive Vastu consultation for homes, offices, shops, and plots. Drawing from classical texts like the Manasara and Mayamata, combined with practical experience, Panditji analyzes the directional alignment of entrances, the placement of rooms and functions, energy flow patterns, and the balance of the Pancha Tatva (five elements) within your space.\\n\\nUnlike generalized Vastu tips, a professional consultation identifies specific Vastu Doshas (imbalances) in your property and provides targeted remedies. These may range from simple adjustments — like repositioning furniture or changing color schemes — to deeper corrections involving room usage changes or placement of Vastu yantras. The goal is always maximum benefit with minimum disruption.\\n\\nWhether you're building a new home, moving into a new office, or experiencing unexplained challenges in your current space, a Vastu consultation can identify the energetic root cause and provide actionable solutions.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Harmonized living and working spaces for positive energy flow\",\n    \"Identification and correction of Vastu Doshas causing problems\",\n    \"Enhanced prosperity, health, and relationship harmony\",\n    \"Practical, implementable remedies (not always structural changes)\",\n    \"New construction guidance for Vastu-compliant design from the start\",\n    \"Peace of mind through balanced, harmonious environments\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Initial Assessment\", \"description\": \"Share property type, floor plan, and any specific concerns via phone/email.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"On-Site Visit or Remote Analysis\", \"description\": \"In-person compass readings and space evaluation, or remote analysis using floor plans with accurate directional markings.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Detailed Report\", \"description\": \"Room-by-room Vastu assessment identifying doshas and imbalances.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Remedies & Solutions\", \"description\": \"Practical, prioritized recommendations tailored to your property.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Follow-Up Support\", \"description\": \"Guidance during implementation and effectiveness monitoring.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Does Vastu require demolishing or rebuilding my home?\",\n      \"answer\": \"No. Most Vastu remedies involve non-structural changes like repositioning furniture, adjusting colors, placing specific items, or changing room functions. Structural changes are recommended only in severe cases.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can Vastu be applied to rented properties?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Absolutely. Many effective Vastu remedies are portable — using colors, placement of objects, crystals, and yantras — making them ideal for rented spaces.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is online Vastu consultation effective?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes, provided accurate floor plans with directional markings are shared. Panditji can conduct thorough analysis remotely, making it accessible for clients worldwide.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"vastu shastra\", \"vastu consultant\", \"home vastu\", \"office vastu\", \"vastu tips\", \"vastu remedies\", \"vastu dosha\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"वास्तु शास्त्र\", \"वास्तु सलाहकार\", \"घर का वास्तु\", \"वास्तु दोष\", \"वास्तु उपाय\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"વાસ્તુ શાસ્ત્ર\", \"વાસ્તુ સલાહકાર\", \"ઘરનું વાસ્તુ\", \"વાસ્તુ દોષ\", \"વાસ્તુ ઉપાય\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"pancha-tatva-balancing\", \"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"Vastu Tips for Your Home: Room-by-Room Guide\",\n    \"Vastu for Office: Boost Productivity with Directional Alignment\",\n    \"Common Vastu Doshas and Their Simple Remedies\",\n    \"Vastu vs Feng Shui: Similarities and Differences\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":387,"cache_read_input_tokens":81254,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":387,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"71c089ee-7aac-4dbd-9d2c-7045c140ee8a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WD5F6AAC9n4uj6c18zfrMu","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/vastu-consultation.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"593d2ad2-be26-4809-8273-7fa1e456360d","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/vastu-consultation.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"vastu-consultation\",\n  \"title\": \"Vastu Consultation\",\n  \"slug\": \"vastu-consultation\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"home\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Harmonize your living and working spaces with ancient Vastu Shastra principles for positive energy flow, prosperity, and peace.\",\n  \"description\": \"Vastu Shastra — the ancient Indian science of architecture and spatial harmony — teaches that the energy flow within your living and working spaces profoundly influences your health, prosperity, relationships, and peace of mind. Like a cosmic version of environmental design, Vastu aligns your physical spaces with the five fundamental elements (earth, water, fire, air, and space) and the eight cardinal directions.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi offers comprehensive Vastu consultation for homes, offices, shops, and plots. Drawing from classical texts like the Manasara and Mayamata, combined with practical experience, Panditji analyzes the directional alignment of entrances, the placement of rooms and functions, energy flow patterns, and the balance of the Pancha Tatva (five elements) within your space.\\n\\nUnlike generalized Vastu tips, a professional consultation identifies specific Vastu Doshas (imbalances) in your property and provides targeted remedies. These may range from simple adjustments — like repositioning furniture or changing color schemes — to deeper corrections involving room usage changes or placement of Vastu yantras. The goal is always maximum benefit with minimum disruption.\\n\\nWhether you're building a new home, moving into a new office, or experiencing unexplained challenges in your current space, a Vastu consultation can identify the energetic root cause and provide actionable solutions.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Harmonized living and working spaces for positive energy flow\",\n    \"Identification and correction of Vastu Doshas causing problems\",\n    \"Enhanced prosperity, health, and relationship harmony\",\n    \"Practical, implementable remedies (not always structural changes)\",\n    \"New construction guidance for Vastu-compliant design from the start\",\n    \"Peace of mind through balanced, harmonious environments\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Initial Assessment\", \"description\": \"Share property type, floor plan, and any specific concerns via phone/email.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"On-Site Visit or Remote Analysis\", \"description\": \"In-person compass readings and space evaluation, or remote analysis using floor plans with accurate directional markings.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Detailed Report\", \"description\": \"Room-by-room Vastu assessment identifying doshas and imbalances.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Remedies & Solutions\", \"description\": \"Practical, prioritized recommendations tailored to your property.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Follow-Up Support\", \"description\": \"Guidance during implementation and effectiveness monitoring.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Does Vastu require demolishing or rebuilding my home?\",\n      \"answer\": \"No. Most Vastu remedies involve non-structural changes like repositioning furniture, adjusting colors, placing specific items, or changing room functions. Structural changes are recommended only in severe cases.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can Vastu be applied to rented properties?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Absolutely. Many effective Vastu remedies are portable — using colors, placement of objects, crystals, and yantras — making them ideal for rented spaces.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is online Vastu consultation effective?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes, provided accurate floor plans with directional markings are shared. Panditji can conduct thorough analysis remotely, making it accessible for clients worldwide.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"vastu shastra\", \"vastu consultant\", \"home vastu\", \"office vastu\", \"vastu tips\", \"vastu remedies\", \"vastu dosha\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"वास्तु शास्त्र\", \"वास्तु सलाहकार\", \"घर का वास्तु\", \"वास्तु दोष\", \"वास्तु उपाय\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"વાસ્તુ શાસ્ત્ર\", \"વાસ્તુ સલાહકાર\", \"ઘરનું વાસ્તુ\", \"વાસ્તુ દોષ\", \"વાસ્તુ ઉપાય\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"pancha-tatva-balancing\", \"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"Vastu Tips for Your Home: Room-by-Room Guide\",\n    \"Vastu for Office: Boost Productivity with Directional Alignment\",\n    \"Common Vastu Doshas and Their Simple Remedies\",\n    \"Vastu vs Feng Shui: Similarities and Differences\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RS8FKf8LXXdG9v5jXXKGW1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WhwifH78YwJ38KMsenEzXR","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/gemstone-recommendations.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"gemstone-recommendations\",\n  \"title\": \"Gemstone Recommendations\",\n  \"slug\": \"gemstone-recommendations\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"gem\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Personalized Jyotish gemstone prescriptions based on your birth chart — the Navratna and their planetary powers for life enhancement.\",\n  \"description\": \"In Vedic astrology, gemstones (Ratna) are among the most powerful remedial tools. Each of the nine primary gemstones — the Navratna — corresponds to a specific planet and channels its cosmic energy when worn correctly. A Ruby amplifies the Sun's vitality, a Pearl soothes the Moon's emotional currents, a Yellow Sapphire expands Jupiter's wisdom, and so on.\\n\\nHowever, gemstone recommendation is not one-size-fits-all. A gemstone that brings tremendous benefit to one person can create difficulties for another. The Anukula (favorable) system requires careful analysis of your complete birth chart — not just your zodiac sign — to determine which planets are your functional benefics, which are creating challenges, and which gemstones will create the most positive shift in your life.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi's gemstone consultation begins with a thorough Kundli analysis, evaluating your Lagna, planetary strengths through Shadbala, current Mahadasha and Antardasha periods, and the specific life areas you wish to strengthen. Only then is a gemstone prescribed — with guidance on quality standards, ideal weight (carat), the correct metal for setting, the auspicious day and time (Muhurta) to first wear it, and the activation mantra.\\n\\nThe Navratna gemstones and their planetary associations: Ruby (Sun), Pearl (Moon), Red Coral (Mars), Emerald (Mercury), Yellow Sapphire (Jupiter), Diamond (Venus), Blue Sapphire (Saturn), Hessonite (Rahu), and Cat's Eye (Ketu). Secondary gemstones are also available as more affordable alternatives.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Strengthened favorable planetary influences in your chart\",\n    \"Reduced impact of malefic planetary periods\",\n    \"Enhanced mental clarity, emotional stability, and focus\",\n    \"Support for specific life goals — career, relationships, health, wealth\",\n    \"Safe, non-invasive remedial approach with centuries of tradition\",\n    \"Continuous benefit as long as the gemstone is worn\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Birth Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Thorough review of your Kundli to identify benefic and malefic planets.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Current Period Assessment\", \"description\": \"Analysis of your active Mahadasha/Antardasha to determine timing relevance.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Gemstone Prescription\", \"description\": \"Specific gemstone recommendation with exact specifications (type, weight, quality, metal).\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Wearing Instructions\", \"description\": \"Muhurta (auspicious timing), finger, hand, and activation mantra for first wearing.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Quality Guidance\", \"description\": \"Advice on sourcing genuine, high-quality gemstones and avoiding treated or synthetic stones.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can wearing the wrong gemstone be harmful?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes. Each gemstone amplifies the energy of its corresponding planet. If that planet is a functional malefic in your chart, wearing its gemstone can intensify negative effects. This is why expert consultation is essential.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can I wear multiple gemstones together?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Only gemstones of friendly planets should be worn together. Gemstones of planets with natural enmity should not be combined. Panditji will advise on compatible combinations.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How long does it take for a gemstone to show effects?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Most people begin to notice subtle shifts within 30-45 days of correctly wearing a gemstone. Full effects typically manifest over 3-6 months.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"gemstone astrology\", \"jyotish ratna\", \"navratna\", \"lucky stone by birth\", \"gemstone recommendation\", \"neelam\", \"pukhraj\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"रत्न ज्योतिष\", \"नवरत्न\", \"भाग्यशाली रत्न\", \"राशि रत्न\", \"नीलम\", \"पुखराज\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"રત્ન જ્યોતિષ\", \"નવરત્ન\", \"ભાગ્યશાળી રત્ન\", \"રાશિ રત્ન\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The Navratna Guide: 9 Gemstones and Their Planetary Powers\",\n    \"How to Choose the Right Gemstone According to Your Kundli\",\n    \"Can Wearing the Wrong Gemstone Be Harmful? Myths vs Reality\",\n    \"Blue Sapphire (Neelam): The Most Powerful and Dangerous Gemstone?\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6017,"cache_read_input_tokens":81641,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6017,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"5eea216d-7ac1-46f0-8628-865c84f3d867"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WhwifH78YwJ38KMsenEzXR","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/gemstone-recommendations.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"48ab164a-d522-4fdf-9e38-5f74754d5d5f","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/gemstone-recommendations.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"gemstone-recommendations\",\n  \"title\": \"Gemstone Recommendations\",\n  \"slug\": \"gemstone-recommendations\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"gem\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Personalized Jyotish gemstone prescriptions based on your birth chart — the Navratna and their planetary powers for life enhancement.\",\n  \"description\": \"In Vedic astrology, gemstones (Ratna) are among the most powerful remedial tools. Each of the nine primary gemstones — the Navratna — corresponds to a specific planet and channels its cosmic energy when worn correctly. A Ruby amplifies the Sun's vitality, a Pearl soothes the Moon's emotional currents, a Yellow Sapphire expands Jupiter's wisdom, and so on.\\n\\nHowever, gemstone recommendation is not one-size-fits-all. A gemstone that brings tremendous benefit to one person can create difficulties for another. The Anukula (favorable) system requires careful analysis of your complete birth chart — not just your zodiac sign — to determine which planets are your functional benefics, which are creating challenges, and which gemstones will create the most positive shift in your life.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi's gemstone consultation begins with a thorough Kundli analysis, evaluating your Lagna, planetary strengths through Shadbala, current Mahadasha and Antardasha periods, and the specific life areas you wish to strengthen. Only then is a gemstone prescribed — with guidance on quality standards, ideal weight (carat), the correct metal for setting, the auspicious day and time (Muhurta) to first wear it, and the activation mantra.\\n\\nThe Navratna gemstones and their planetary associations: Ruby (Sun), Pearl (Moon), Red Coral (Mars), Emerald (Mercury), Yellow Sapphire (Jupiter), Diamond (Venus), Blue Sapphire (Saturn), Hessonite (Rahu), and Cat's Eye (Ketu). Secondary gemstones are also available as more affordable alternatives.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Strengthened favorable planetary influences in your chart\",\n    \"Reduced impact of malefic planetary periods\",\n    \"Enhanced mental clarity, emotional stability, and focus\",\n    \"Support for specific life goals — career, relationships, health, wealth\",\n    \"Safe, non-invasive remedial approach with centuries of tradition\",\n    \"Continuous benefit as long as the gemstone is worn\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Birth Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Thorough review of your Kundli to identify benefic and malefic planets.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Current Period Assessment\", \"description\": \"Analysis of your active Mahadasha/Antardasha to determine timing relevance.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Gemstone Prescription\", \"description\": \"Specific gemstone recommendation with exact specifications (type, weight, quality, metal).\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Wearing Instructions\", \"description\": \"Muhurta (auspicious timing), finger, hand, and activation mantra for first wearing.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Quality Guidance\", \"description\": \"Advice on sourcing genuine, high-quality gemstones and avoiding treated or synthetic stones.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can wearing the wrong gemstone be harmful?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes. Each gemstone amplifies the energy of its corresponding planet. If that planet is a functional malefic in your chart, wearing its gemstone can intensify negative effects. This is why expert consultation is essential.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can I wear multiple gemstones together?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Only gemstones of friendly planets should be worn together. Gemstones of planets with natural enmity should not be combined. Panditji will advise on compatible combinations.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How long does it take for a gemstone to show effects?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Most people begin to notice subtle shifts within 30-45 days of correctly wearing a gemstone. Full effects typically manifest over 3-6 months.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"gemstone astrology\", \"jyotish ratna\", \"navratna\", \"lucky stone by birth\", \"gemstone recommendation\", \"neelam\", \"pukhraj\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"रत्न ज्योतिष\", \"नवरत्न\", \"भाग्यशाली रत्न\", \"राशि रत्न\", \"नीलम\", \"पुखराज\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"રત્ન જ્યોતિષ\", \"નવરત્ન\", \"ભાગ્યશાળી રત્ન\", \"રાશિ રત્ન\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The Navratna Guide: 9 Gemstones and Their Planetary Powers\",\n    \"How to Choose the Right Gemstone According to Your Kundli\",\n    \"Can Wearing the Wrong Gemstone Be Harmful? Myths vs Reality\",\n    \"Blue Sapphire (Neelam): The Most Powerful and Dangerous Gemstone?\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RS8FKf8LXXdG9v5jXXKGW1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01AP9zrtycUDUWKhJ3JAampd","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/karma-life-purpose-counselling.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\",\n  \"title\": \"Karma & Life-Purpose Counselling\",\n  \"slug\": \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"lotus\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Explore your soul's journey — understand karmic patterns, life purpose, and Dharmic path through deep Vedic astrological insight.\",\n  \"description\": \"At the deepest level, Vedic astrology is not about prediction — it's about understanding the soul's journey. Karma and Life-Purpose Counselling explores the profound questions: Why am I here? What karmic patterns am I carrying? What is my Dharma — my true life path?\\n\\nVedic astrology recognizes three types of karma that shape your life: Sanchita Karma (the accumulated bank of past-life actions), Prarabdha Karma (the portion allocated for this lifetime, reflected in your birth chart), and Kriyamana Karma (the new karma you create through present choices). Your birth chart is essentially a map of your Prarabdha — the karmic lessons, opportunities, and challenges destined for this life.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi draws on 20+ years of experience in Vedic astrology and spiritual consultation to guide you through this profound self-exploration. Through analysis of Rahu and Ketu (the lunar nodes — your karmic axis), Saturn's placement (the karmic taskmaster), the 12th house (past-life patterns), and the 9th house (Dharma and life purpose), Panditji illuminates the deeper spiritual narrative behind your life experiences.\\n\\nThis counselling is particularly valuable during life transitions — when career success feels hollow, relationships repeatedly challenge the same patterns, or a growing inner voice seeks something more meaningful. It provides not just understanding, but actionable steps: remedial practices, meditation techniques, mantras, and lifestyle adjustments that accelerate spiritual growth while honoring your karmic path.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Clarity on your soul's purpose and Dharmic path\",\n    \"Understanding of recurring life patterns through a karmic lens\",\n    \"Release from confusion during major life transitions\",\n    \"Practical spiritual practices tailored to your chart\",\n    \"Peace through acceptance of karmic lessons\",\n    \"Empowerment through Kriyamana Karma — shaping your future through conscious action\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Deep Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Focus on karmic indicators — Rahu/Ketu axis, Saturn, 9th and 12th houses, Nakshatras.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Life Pattern Discussion\", \"description\": \"Open conversation about recurring themes, challenges, and questions in your life.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Karmic Narrative\", \"description\": \"Panditji weaves together the astrological insights into a coherent spiritual narrative.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Dharma Path Guidance\", \"description\": \"Specific guidance on aligning daily life with your soul's purpose.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Spiritual Practices\", \"description\": \"Customized mantras, meditation, and remedial actions for spiritual acceleration.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can I change my karma?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Prarabdha Karma (this life's allocation) is fixed, but how you respond to it creates Kriyamana Karma — new karma. Through conscious action, spiritual practice, and selfless service, you can mitigate negative karma and build positive karmic credit.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is this different from a regular Kundli reading?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes. While a Kundli reading covers practical life areas, Karma Counselling goes deeper into the spiritual dimension — past-life patterns, soul purpose, and the 'why' behind your life's circumstances.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Do I need to believe in reincarnation for this to be useful?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Not necessarily. Even without a belief in past lives, the framework of karmic patterns provides valuable insight into recurring behavioral patterns, psychological tendencies, and a sense of life direction.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"karma astrology\", \"life purpose astrology\", \"past life karma\", \"spiritual counselling\", \"dharma path\", \"karmic astrology\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"कर्म ज्योतिष\", \"जीवन उद्देश्य\", \"पूर्व जन्म कर्म\", \"आध्यात्मिक मार्गदर्शन\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"કર્મ જ્યોતિષ\", \"જીવન ઉદ્દેશ્ય\", \"પૂર્વ જન્મ કર્મ\", \"આધ્યાત્મિક માર્ગદર્શન\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"seven-chakras-balancing\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"Understanding Karma in Vedic Astrology: Sanchita, Prarabdha, and Kriyamana\",\n    \"Rahu and Ketu: Your Past Life Karma Decoded\",\n    \"Can You Change Your Destiny? Free Will vs Fate in Jyotish\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6017,"cache_read_input_tokens":81641,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6017,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"e696719f-ed11-4526-8855-5a2187bb1591"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AP9zrtycUDUWKhJ3JAampd","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/karma-life-purpose-counselling.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"4293405b-6662-4c5e-bec5-c94c352b1af5","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/karma-life-purpose-counselling.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\",\n  \"title\": \"Karma & Life-Purpose Counselling\",\n  \"slug\": \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\",\n  \"category\": \"core\",\n  \"icon\": \"lotus\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Explore your soul's journey — understand karmic patterns, life purpose, and Dharmic path through deep Vedic astrological insight.\",\n  \"description\": \"At the deepest level, Vedic astrology is not about prediction — it's about understanding the soul's journey. Karma and Life-Purpose Counselling explores the profound questions: Why am I here? What karmic patterns am I carrying? What is my Dharma — my true life path?\\n\\nVedic astrology recognizes three types of karma that shape your life: Sanchita Karma (the accumulated bank of past-life actions), Prarabdha Karma (the portion allocated for this lifetime, reflected in your birth chart), and Kriyamana Karma (the new karma you create through present choices). Your birth chart is essentially a map of your Prarabdha — the karmic lessons, opportunities, and challenges destined for this life.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi draws on 20+ years of experience in Vedic astrology and spiritual consultation to guide you through this profound self-exploration. Through analysis of Rahu and Ketu (the lunar nodes — your karmic axis), Saturn's placement (the karmic taskmaster), the 12th house (past-life patterns), and the 9th house (Dharma and life purpose), Panditji illuminates the deeper spiritual narrative behind your life experiences.\\n\\nThis counselling is particularly valuable during life transitions — when career success feels hollow, relationships repeatedly challenge the same patterns, or a growing inner voice seeks something more meaningful. It provides not just understanding, but actionable steps: remedial practices, meditation techniques, mantras, and lifestyle adjustments that accelerate spiritual growth while honoring your karmic path.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Clarity on your soul's purpose and Dharmic path\",\n    \"Understanding of recurring life patterns through a karmic lens\",\n    \"Release from confusion during major life transitions\",\n    \"Practical spiritual practices tailored to your chart\",\n    \"Peace through acceptance of karmic lessons\",\n    \"Empowerment through Kriyamana Karma — shaping your future through conscious action\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Deep Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Focus on karmic indicators — Rahu/Ketu axis, Saturn, 9th and 12th houses, Nakshatras.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Life Pattern Discussion\", \"description\": \"Open conversation about recurring themes, challenges, and questions in your life.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Karmic Narrative\", \"description\": \"Panditji weaves together the astrological insights into a coherent spiritual narrative.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Dharma Path Guidance\", \"description\": \"Specific guidance on aligning daily life with your soul's purpose.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Spiritual Practices\", \"description\": \"Customized mantras, meditation, and remedial actions for spiritual acceleration.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can I change my karma?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Prarabdha Karma (this life's allocation) is fixed, but how you respond to it creates Kriyamana Karma — new karma. Through conscious action, spiritual practice, and selfless service, you can mitigate negative karma and build positive karmic credit.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Is this different from a regular Kundli reading?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes. While a Kundli reading covers practical life areas, Karma Counselling goes deeper into the spiritual dimension — past-life patterns, soul purpose, and the 'why' behind your life's circumstances.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Do I need to believe in reincarnation for this to be useful?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Not necessarily. Even without a belief in past lives, the framework of karmic patterns provides valuable insight into recurring behavioral patterns, psychological tendencies, and a sense of life direction.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"karma astrology\", \"life purpose astrology\", \"past life karma\", \"spiritual counselling\", \"dharma path\", \"karmic astrology\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"कर्म ज्योतिष\", \"जीवन उद्देश्य\", \"पूर्व जन्म कर्म\", \"आध्यात्मिक मार्गदर्शन\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"કર્મ જ્યોતિષ\", \"જીવન ઉદ્દેશ્ય\", \"પૂર્વ જન્મ કર્મ\", \"આધ્યાત્મિક માર્ગદર્શન\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\", \"seven-chakras-balancing\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"Understanding Karma in Vedic Astrology: Sanchita, Prarabdha, and Kriyamana\",\n    \"Rahu and Ketu: Your Past Life Karma Decoded\",\n    \"Can You Change Your Destiny? Free Will vs Fate in Jyotish\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RS8FKf8LXXdG9v5jXXKGW1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011bcLXJzxqTL5gQfTFircKH","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/pancha-tatva-balancing.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"pancha-tatva-balancing\",\n  \"title\": \"Pancha Tatva Balancing\",\n  \"slug\": \"pancha-tatva-balancing\",\n  \"category\": \"spiritual\",\n  \"icon\": \"elements\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Harmonize the five fundamental elements — Earth, Water, Fire, Air, and Space — within your body and environment for holistic wellbeing.\",\n  \"description\": \"Pancha Tatva — the five fundamental elements of Vedic science — forms the building blocks of all creation: Prithvi (Earth), Jal (Water), Agni (Fire), Vayu (Air), and Akash (Space/Ether). Every living being, every space, and even the planets themselves are composed of these five elements in varying proportions. When they are in balance, there is health, prosperity, and peace. When imbalanced, challenges arise in body, mind, and environment.\\n\\nIn the Vedic tradition, the Pancha Tatva Siddantha is one of the most important doctrines connecting astrology, Ayurveda, and yoga. Each zodiac sign carries an elemental signature — Aries, Leo, and Sagittarius are fire signs; Taurus, Virgo, and Capricorn are earth signs — and the five planets Mercury, Venus, Mars, Jupiter, and Saturn each govern one of the five elements.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi analyzes your birth chart to determine your elemental constitution — which elements are dominant, which are deficient, and how the current planetary transits are affecting your elemental balance. This analysis connects three interconnected systems: Vedic astrology (for diagnosis), Ayurveda (for physical remedies), and Yoga (for energetic practices) — forming a tripod of holistic wellbeing.\\n\\nRemedies for elemental imbalance may include specific dietary recommendations, color therapy, directional adjustments in your living space (connecting to Vastu), mantras that activate deficient elements, and yoga practices targeting the chakras associated with each element.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Holistic diagnosis connecting astrology, Ayurveda, and yoga\",\n    \"Understanding of your elemental constitution and personality traits\",\n    \"Physical health improvement through elemental balance\",\n    \"Emotional stability through harmonized elements\",\n    \"Environmental harmony through Vastu-aligned elemental corrections\",\n    \"Integrated remedies spanning diet, color, mantra, and lifestyle\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Elemental Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Your birth chart is analyzed for elemental distribution across signs, houses, and planets.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Imbalance Identification\", \"description\": \"Specific elemental excesses and deficiencies are mapped.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Holistic Assessment\", \"description\": \"Integration with Ayurvedic body type (Prakriti) and current health patterns.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Customized Remedies\", \"description\": \"Multi-dimensional remedies spanning diet, yoga, mantra, color, and Vastu.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Follow-Up\", \"description\": \"Monitoring effectiveness and adjusting remedies as needed.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How is Pancha Tatva different from Vastu Consultation?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Vastu focuses on your external space. Pancha Tatva focuses on the elemental balance within your body and mind, though they overlap — both use directional alignment and elemental harmony.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"What are the signs of elemental imbalance?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Excess fire manifests as anger and inflammation. Excess earth as rigidity and lethargy. Excess water as emotional overwhelm. Deficient air as stagnation. Deficient space as feeling confined.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"pancha tatva\", \"five elements balancing\", \"prithvi jal agni vayu akash\", \"elemental healing\", \"five elements astrology\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"पंच तत्व\", \"पांच तत्व संतुलन\", \"पृथ्वी जल अग्नि वायु आकाश\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"પંચ તત્વ\", \"પાંચ તત્વ સંતુલન\", \"પૃથ્વી જળ અગ્નિ વાયુ આકાશ\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"seven-chakras-balancing\", \"vastu-consultation\", \"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The Five Elements of Vedic Science: A Guide to Pancha Tatva\",\n    \"How the Five Elements Affect Your Health and Personality\",\n    \"Balancing Earth, Water, Fire, Air, and Space in Daily Life\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6017,"cache_read_input_tokens":81641,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6017,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"1f4110c3-739e-4fb9-9aa7-286e29ed991b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011bcLXJzxqTL5gQfTFircKH","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/pancha-tatva-balancing.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"5f48534a-42da-4269-a2d6-2f5f5a0f09b4","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/pancha-tatva-balancing.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"pancha-tatva-balancing\",\n  \"title\": \"Pancha Tatva Balancing\",\n  \"slug\": \"pancha-tatva-balancing\",\n  \"category\": \"spiritual\",\n  \"icon\": \"elements\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Harmonize the five fundamental elements — Earth, Water, Fire, Air, and Space — within your body and environment for holistic wellbeing.\",\n  \"description\": \"Pancha Tatva — the five fundamental elements of Vedic science — forms the building blocks of all creation: Prithvi (Earth), Jal (Water), Agni (Fire), Vayu (Air), and Akash (Space/Ether). Every living being, every space, and even the planets themselves are composed of these five elements in varying proportions. When they are in balance, there is health, prosperity, and peace. When imbalanced, challenges arise in body, mind, and environment.\\n\\nIn the Vedic tradition, the Pancha Tatva Siddantha is one of the most important doctrines connecting astrology, Ayurveda, and yoga. Each zodiac sign carries an elemental signature — Aries, Leo, and Sagittarius are fire signs; Taurus, Virgo, and Capricorn are earth signs — and the five planets Mercury, Venus, Mars, Jupiter, and Saturn each govern one of the five elements.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi analyzes your birth chart to determine your elemental constitution — which elements are dominant, which are deficient, and how the current planetary transits are affecting your elemental balance. This analysis connects three interconnected systems: Vedic astrology (for diagnosis), Ayurveda (for physical remedies), and Yoga (for energetic practices) — forming a tripod of holistic wellbeing.\\n\\nRemedies for elemental imbalance may include specific dietary recommendations, color therapy, directional adjustments in your living space (connecting to Vastu), mantras that activate deficient elements, and yoga practices targeting the chakras associated with each element.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Holistic diagnosis connecting astrology, Ayurveda, and yoga\",\n    \"Understanding of your elemental constitution and personality traits\",\n    \"Physical health improvement through elemental balance\",\n    \"Emotional stability through harmonized elements\",\n    \"Environmental harmony through Vastu-aligned elemental corrections\",\n    \"Integrated remedies spanning diet, color, mantra, and lifestyle\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Elemental Chart Analysis\", \"description\": \"Your birth chart is analyzed for elemental distribution across signs, houses, and planets.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Imbalance Identification\", \"description\": \"Specific elemental excesses and deficiencies are mapped.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Holistic Assessment\", \"description\": \"Integration with Ayurvedic body type (Prakriti) and current health patterns.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Customized Remedies\", \"description\": \"Multi-dimensional remedies spanning diet, yoga, mantra, color, and Vastu.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Follow-Up\", \"description\": \"Monitoring effectiveness and adjusting remedies as needed.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How is Pancha Tatva different from Vastu Consultation?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Vastu focuses on your external space. Pancha Tatva focuses on the elemental balance within your body and mind, though they overlap — both use directional alignment and elemental harmony.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"What are the signs of elemental imbalance?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Excess fire manifests as anger and inflammation. Excess earth as rigidity and lethargy. Excess water as emotional overwhelm. Deficient air as stagnation. Deficient space as feeling confined.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"pancha tatva\", \"five elements balancing\", \"prithvi jal agni vayu akash\", \"elemental healing\", \"five elements astrology\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"पंच तत्व\", \"पांच तत्व संतुलन\", \"पृथ्वी जल अग्नि वायु आकाश\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"પંચ તત્વ\", \"પાંચ તત્વ સંતુલન\", \"પૃથ્વી જળ અગ્નિ વાયુ આકાશ\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"seven-chakras-balancing\", \"vastu-consultation\", \"vedic-astrology-kundli-reading\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The Five Elements of Vedic Science: A Guide to Pancha Tatva\",\n    \"How the Five Elements Affect Your Health and Personality\",\n    \"Balancing Earth, Water, Fire, Air, and Space in Daily Life\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RS8FKf8LXXdG9v5jXXKGW1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WbAdKSVLV9hEuYNDiZcRpj","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/seven-chakras-balancing.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"seven-chakras-balancing\",\n  \"title\": \"Seven Chakras Balancing\",\n  \"slug\": \"seven-chakras-balancing\",\n  \"category\": \"spiritual\",\n  \"icon\": \"chakra\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Align your seven energy centers through an integrated approach combining Vedic astrology, mantras, meditation, and gemstones.\",\n  \"description\": \"The seven chakras are energy centers located along the spine, from its base to the crown of the head. According to ancient Hindu philosophy, these spinning wheels of energy govern different aspects of your physical, emotional, and spiritual wellbeing. When all seven chakras are open and balanced, energy (Prana) flows freely, creating vitality, clarity, and inner peace. When blocked or imbalanced, the corresponding life areas suffer.\\n\\nWhat makes Believe Astrology's approach unique is the integration of chakra healing with Vedic astrology. Each chakra corresponds to specific planets and zodiac signs: Mars rules the Root Chakra (survival and stability), the Sun governs the Heart Chakra (identity and love), and Mercury rules the Throat Chakra (communication and expression). Your birth chart reveals which chakras are naturally strong, which may be challenged, and which planets are influencing your energy flow.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi combines this astrological diagnosis with targeted healing practices. For each imbalanced chakra, specific Vedic remedies are prescribed: planetary mantras that resonate with the chakra's frequency, meditation techniques, appropriate gemstones, Ayurvedic herbs and oils, dietary adjustments, and yoga asanas.\\n\\nThe seven chakras and their domains: Muladhara (Root — security), Svadhisthana (Sacral — creativity), Manipura (Solar Plexus — power), Anahata (Heart — love), Vishuddha (Throat — communication), Ajna (Third Eye — intuition), and Sahasrara (Crown — spiritual connection).\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Improved physical health through energetic alignment\",\n    \"Emotional stability and stronger relationships\",\n    \"Enhanced intuition and mental clarity\",\n    \"Deeper spiritual connection and purpose\",\n    \"Astrologically-informed healing — targeted and precise\",\n    \"Integrated approach combining mantras, gems, yoga, and meditation\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Astrological-Chakra Mapping\", \"description\": \"Your birth chart is analyzed for planetary influences on each chakra.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Blockage Identification\", \"description\": \"Specific chakras showing weakness or over-activation are identified.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Symptom Correlation\", \"description\": \"Connecting your reported physical/emotional concerns with chakra imbalances.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Healing Protocol\", \"description\": \"Customized combination of mantras, meditations, gemstones, and practices for each affected chakra.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Ongoing Practice\", \"description\": \"A daily routine you can follow independently, with periodic check-ins.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can blocked chakras cause physical illness?\",\n      \"answer\": \"In the Vedic framework, prolonged energetic imbalance can manifest as physical symptoms. Chakra work is complementary to medical care, not a replacement.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How long does chakra balancing take?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Initial improvements can be felt within weeks of consistent practice. Deep, lasting balance develops over months of regular meditation, mantra chanting, and lifestyle alignment.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"chakra balancing\", \"seven chakras healing\", \"kundalini\", \"energy healing\", \"chakra meditation\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"सात चक्र\", \"चक्र संतुलन\", \"कुंडलिनी\", \"ऊर्जा चिकित्सा\", \"चक्र ध्यान\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"સાત ચક્ર\", \"ચક્ર સંતુલન\", \"કુંડલિની\", \"ઊર્જા ચિકિત્સા\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"pancha-tatva-balancing\", \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The 7 Chakras Explained: A Complete Guide for Beginners\",\n    \"How Blocked Chakras Affect Your Health and Relationships\",\n    \"Astrology and Chakras: How Planets Influence Your Energy Centers\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6017,"cache_read_input_tokens":81641,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6017,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"362c4dc3-e1e6-4b06-bf6b-217ac99c3460"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WbAdKSVLV9hEuYNDiZcRpj","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/seven-chakras-balancing.json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"cfb3d389-4e50-4299-9650-9ff0e80ac716","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/seven-chakras-balancing.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"seven-chakras-balancing\",\n  \"title\": \"Seven Chakras Balancing\",\n  \"slug\": \"seven-chakras-balancing\",\n  \"category\": \"spiritual\",\n  \"icon\": \"chakra\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Align your seven energy centers through an integrated approach combining Vedic astrology, mantras, meditation, and gemstones.\",\n  \"description\": \"The seven chakras are energy centers located along the spine, from its base to the crown of the head. According to ancient Hindu philosophy, these spinning wheels of energy govern different aspects of your physical, emotional, and spiritual wellbeing. When all seven chakras are open and balanced, energy (Prana) flows freely, creating vitality, clarity, and inner peace. When blocked or imbalanced, the corresponding life areas suffer.\\n\\nWhat makes Believe Astrology's approach unique is the integration of chakra healing with Vedic astrology. Each chakra corresponds to specific planets and zodiac signs: Mars rules the Root Chakra (survival and stability), the Sun governs the Heart Chakra (identity and love), and Mercury rules the Throat Chakra (communication and expression). Your birth chart reveals which chakras are naturally strong, which may be challenged, and which planets are influencing your energy flow.\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi combines this astrological diagnosis with targeted healing practices. For each imbalanced chakra, specific Vedic remedies are prescribed: planetary mantras that resonate with the chakra's frequency, meditation techniques, appropriate gemstones, Ayurvedic herbs and oils, dietary adjustments, and yoga asanas.\\n\\nThe seven chakras and their domains: Muladhara (Root — security), Svadhisthana (Sacral — creativity), Manipura (Solar Plexus — power), Anahata (Heart — love), Vishuddha (Throat — communication), Ajna (Third Eye — intuition), and Sahasrara (Crown — spiritual connection).\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Improved physical health through energetic alignment\",\n    \"Emotional stability and stronger relationships\",\n    \"Enhanced intuition and mental clarity\",\n    \"Deeper spiritual connection and purpose\",\n    \"Astrologically-informed healing — targeted and precise\",\n    \"Integrated approach combining mantras, gems, yoga, and meditation\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Astrological-Chakra Mapping\", \"description\": \"Your birth chart is analyzed for planetary influences on each chakra.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Blockage Identification\", \"description\": \"Specific chakras showing weakness or over-activation are identified.\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Symptom Correlation\", \"description\": \"Connecting your reported physical/emotional concerns with chakra imbalances.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Healing Protocol\", \"description\": \"Customized combination of mantras, meditations, gemstones, and practices for each affected chakra.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Ongoing Practice\", \"description\": \"A daily routine you can follow independently, with periodic check-ins.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can blocked chakras cause physical illness?\",\n      \"answer\": \"In the Vedic framework, prolonged energetic imbalance can manifest as physical symptoms. Chakra work is complementary to medical care, not a replacement.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How long does chakra balancing take?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Initial improvements can be felt within weeks of consistent practice. Deep, lasting balance develops over months of regular meditation, mantra chanting, and lifestyle alignment.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"chakra balancing\", \"seven chakras healing\", \"kundalini\", \"energy healing\", \"chakra meditation\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"सात चक्र\", \"चक्र संतुलन\", \"कुंडलिनी\", \"ऊर्जा चिकित्सा\", \"चक्र ध्यान\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"સાત ચક્ર\", \"ચક્ર સંતુલન\", \"કુંડલિની\", \"ઊર્જા ચિકિત્સા\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"pancha-tatva-balancing\", \"karma-life-purpose-counselling\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"The 7 Chakras Explained: A Complete Guide for Beginners\",\n    \"How Blocked Chakras Affect Your Health and Relationships\",\n    \"Astrology and Chakras: How Planets Influence Your Energy Centers\"\n  ]\n}","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018EVHmhkgwnw6KBQjrqdm45","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01M66GnE6EYrG1X26pvLKejs","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/s0m0ohl/pers/mahi_astro/.tasks/mahi-astro/content-drafts/services/en/vedic-spiritual-poojas.json","content":"{\n  \"id\": \"vedic-spiritual-poojas\",\n  \"title\": \"Vedic Spiritual Poojas\",\n  \"slug\": \"vedic-spiritual-poojas\",\n  \"category\": \"spiritual\",\n  \"icon\": \"flame\",\n  \"shortDescription\": \"Sacred worship ceremonies rooted in the Vedas — Ganesh, Lakshmi, Navgraha, and specialized Poojas for every life need.\",\n  \"description\": \"Vedic Poojas are sacred worship ceremonies rooted in the ancient Vedas — Hinduism's oldest scriptures. Through a structured sequence of invocations, offerings, mantras, and meditations, a Pooja creates a powerful bridge between the devotee and the divine. It is a path of transformation where the devotee's consciousness is elevated through focused devotion (Bhakti), sacred action (Karma), and spiritual knowledge (Jnana).\\n\\nPandit Shree Mahadev Joshi performs a wide range of Vedic Poojas tailored to specific needs and occasions. From Ganesh Pooja for removing obstacles before new ventures, to Lakshmi Pooja for wealth and prosperity, Saraswati Pooja for wisdom and learning, Navgraha Pooja for planetary harmony, and Shanti Poojas for peace and protection — each ritual follows the authentic Vedic Vidhi (procedure) handed down through generations of priestly tradition.\\n\\nThe four levels of Pooja ritual — from the simple Panchopachar (5 offerings) for daily worship to the elaborate Shodashopachar (16 offerings) for major ceremonies — ensure that the right intensity of ritual matches the devotee's needs and the occasion's significance. When performed by a qualified Pundit with proper Sankalpa (intention), Mantras, and offerings, these rituals draw powerful spiritual energies that purify the environment, bless the participants, and create a protective shield against negative influences.\\n\\nWhether you seek blessings for a new home (Graha Pravesh), success in business (Vyapar Vriddhi), removal of obstacles (Vighna Nivaran), health restoration (Maha Mrityunjaya), or spiritual upliftment, there is a specific Vedic Pooja designed for your purpose.\",\n  \"benefits\": [\n    \"Divine blessings for health, prosperity, and protection\",\n    \"Purification of mind, body, and environment\",\n    \"Reduction of negative planetary influences (Graha Dosha Nivaran)\",\n    \"Spiritual growth and consciousness elevation\",\n    \"Marking auspicious occasions with sacred rituals\",\n    \"Community and family bonding through shared worship\"\n  ],\n  \"process\": [\n    { \"step\": 1, \"title\": \"Need Assessment\", \"description\": \"Discussion of your specific intention, concerns, or the occasion to be celebrated.\" },\n    { \"step\": 2, \"title\": \"Pooja Selection\", \"description\": \"Panditji recommends the appropriate Pooja, level of ritual, and optimal date (Muhurta).\" },\n    { \"step\": 3, \"title\": \"Preparation\", \"description\": \"Guidance on required materials (Samagri), space setup, and participant preparation.\" },\n    { \"step\": 4, \"title\": \"Performance\", \"description\": \"Full Vedic Pooja conducted by Panditji — in-person at your location or at a temple.\" },\n    { \"step\": 5, \"title\": \"Post-Pooja Guidance\", \"description\": \"Instructions on Prasad distribution, maintaining the sanctified space, and follow-up practices.\" }\n  ],\n  \"faqs\": [\n    {\n      \"question\": \"Can Poojas be performed remotely/online?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Yes. Panditji can perform Poojas at a sacred location while you participate via video call. The Sankalpa is taken in your name and Nakshatra, and the Prasad can be shipped to you.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How do I know which Pooja I need?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Share your concern or intention with Panditji. Based on your birth chart and specific situation, the most effective Pooja will be recommended.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"question\": \"How often should Poojas be performed?\",\n      \"answer\": \"Some Poojas are one-time (for specific events), while others benefit from periodic repetition. Special Poojas may be recommended during Dasha transitions, eclipses, or challenging planetary periods.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keywords\": {\n    \"en\": [\"vedic puja\", \"hindu puja service\", \"online puja booking\", \"ganesh puja\", \"lakshmi puja\", \"navgraha puja\"],\n    \"hi\": [\"वैदिक पूजा\", \"हिंदू पूजा\", \"ऑनलाइन पूजा\", \"गणेश पूजा\", \"लक्ष्मी पूजा\", \"नवग्रह पूजा\"],\n    \"gu\": [\"વૈદિક પૂજા\", \"હિંદુ પૂજા\", \"ગણેશ પૂજા\", \"લક્ષ્મી પૂજા\", \"નવગ્રહ પૂજા\"]\n  },\n  \"relatedServices\": [\"vedic-karma-kand-yagnas\", \"maha-mrityunjaya-mantra-anushthan\", \"mantras-chanting\"],\n  \"blogTopics\": [\n    \"Types of Vedic Poojas and When to Perform Them\",\n    \"Navgraha Puja: Balancing All 9 Planets for Harmony\",\n    \"The Spiritual Benefits of Lakshmi Puja for Wealth and Prosperity\"\n  ]\n}"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5734,"cache_read_input_tokens":87658,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5734,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a79b89ba-b90f-477b-8d26-9b7d3a498116","uuid":"c830d0d1-180b-49bc-827c-8e44412208f0"}
